data.name: FLAVEX Naturextrakte
data.description: FLAVEX Naturextrakte GmbH is a pioneer in supercritical fluid extraction, with more than 30 years of experience in high pressure plant design and operation, phytochemistry and development of herbal extracts. Focused on specialty extracts from botanical raw materials, Flavex products are sold worldwide as ingredients to the food and flavor, nutraceuticals, cosmetics, perfumery and aromatherapy industries. From organic contract cultivation to the finished end product, Flavex delivers quality and detailed documentation of all relevant process steps.

data.name: Flavoxan™ 25
data.description: The formulation contains mainly rosemary antioxidant, produced by supercritical fluid extraction with natural carbon dioxide and a small amount of ethanol as entrainer, sunflower oil (organic) for standardizing to a well defined content of effective compounds, sunflower lecithin and a small amount of a natural mixture of GMO free tocopherols.

data.name: Flavex™ Camomile Extract CO2-to, Flower
data.description: Camomile Flower CO2-TO Extract is a green-brown colored liquid at 40ºC with a fine camomile-like smell. Produced by supercritical fluid extraction with natural carbon dioxide, no inorganic salts, no solvent residues, no heavy metals and no reproducible microorganisms. Applications include antiphlogisticum, spasmolyticum, carminativum [3], in skin care products and in natural remedies.

data.name: Flavex™ Seabuckthorn Extract CO2-to, Berries
data.description: Seabuckthorn Berries CO2-TO Extract is an orange-red oil with characteristic seabuckthorn smell, at room temperature a little turbid by some precipitates, stabilized with FLAVEX Rosemary Antioxidant. Seabuckthorn berry oil contains the oil of seabuckthorn pulp and seabuckthorn seeds. Ideal for application in food supplements in case of lack of essential fatty acids, in cosmetics for treatment of skin allergy and skin impurities, in skin caring and regenerating cosmetics.

data.name: Flavex™ Hop Extract CO2-to, Standardized, Flavor Reduced
data.description: Hop CO2-TO Extract Flavor Reduced, Standardized is a brown viscous extract at room temperature, with a weak typical smell and bitter taste. This product is produced by supercritical CO2 extraction with natural carbon dioxide, no solvent residues, no inorganic salts, no heavy metals and no reproducible microorganisms. In a second step the extract is flavor reduced by counter current column extraction with natural carbon dioxide. The extract is standardized with sunflower oil (organic) to a content of 49 - 51 % sum of humulones and lupulones. Ideal for application in the beer industry for flavoring, bittering, in cosmetics for its antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties, as well as in deodorants, skin and foot care products.

data.name: Flavex™ Seabuckthorn Extract CO2-to, Pulp
data.description: Seabuckthorn Pulp CO2-TO Extract is a red oil with characteristic odor, stabilized with FLAVEX Rosemary Antioxidant. It is produced by supercritical fluid extraction with natural carbon dioxide, no solvent residues, no inorganic salts, no heavy metals and no reproducible microorganisms. This product can be applied in the pharmacy industry, in cosmetics for skin care preparations, for wound healing, increasing the granulation, in sun cream for alleviation of sunburn.

data.name: Flavex™ Rosemary Extract CO2-se Plus
data.description: Rosemary CO2-SE-Plus Extract is a clear yellow oil with eucalyptus like, woody - balsamic smell. It is produced by supercritical fluid extraction with natural carbon dioxide and a small amount of pure ethanol as entrainer and with multistep separation, no inorganic salts, no heavy metals and no reproducible microorganisms. Ideal for application in cosmetic products, in creams, bath oils, in perfumery and soap industry, in confectionery and liquor industry, as spice in food industry, in meat and fish products, and in the medical industry for improving blood circulation, varicose veins and muscular pain.

data.name: Flavex™ Vanilla Extract Co2 Ha, Planifolia
data.description: Produced by supercritical fluid extraction with natural carbon dioxide, no solvent residues, no inorganic salts, no heavy metals, no reproducible microorganisms.

data.name: Flavex™ Rosehip Extract CO2-to, Seed, Organic
data.description: Rosehip Seed CO2-TO Extract (organic) is a yellow reddish, clear oil, stabilized with natural FLAVEX Rosemary Antioxidant. This product is produced by supercritical CO2 extraction under use of natural carbon dioxide. It contains no residues, no inorganic salts, no heavy metals and no reproducible microorganisms. Ideal for application in the cosmetic industry in moisturizing creams against dry skin, and antiwrinkle care. Is recommendable in case of impure skin, acne, neurodermitis, scaly and chapped skin. Also finds use as a food additive, supplementing essential fatty acids.
